title: Texas Senate, District 15
text:
District 15 of the <a href="Texas%20Senate">Texas Senate</a> is a senatorial district that currently serves a portion of <a href="Harris%20County%2C%20Texas">Harris</a> county in the <a href="United%20States">U.S.</a> state of <a href="Texas">Texas</a>.
The current Senator from District 15 is <a href="John%20Whitmire">John Whitmire</a>.
Top 4 biggest cities in district.
District 15 has a population of 793,108 with 574,255 that is at voting age from the <a href="2010%20United%20States%20Census">2010 census</a>.
